incident.name: noticing more errors than usual in SSRPM log
incident.description: With new first years onboarding (about 40 in the last 48 hrs) I noticed that we were getting an unusual number of "-71" errors - around a dozen or so in the last 24 hrs (this is an SMS related error, see attached solution). I bumped the number of test SMS messages allowed, from 2 to 3, but my hunch is that something else is causing the errors.
incident.description_no_html: With new first years onboarding (about 40 in the last 48 hrs) I noticed that we were getting an unusual number of "-71" errors - around a dozen or so in the last 24 hrs (this is an SMS related error, see attached solution). I bumped the number of test SMS messages allowed, from 2 to 3, but my hunch is that something else is causing the errors.
incident.resolution_description: I set the number of test SMS to 0, which makes it unlimited. (Service Management..Configure...SMS) That seems to have resolved the issue with our test student.

Lillian

Lillian
